Explanation of Specifics
For Every Additional Element, Why You Are Adding It:
Additional Server: To enhance scalability and provide redundancy.
Clustered Load Balancer: To ensure high availability and balanced traffic.
Split Components: To optimize performance and simplify resource management.
Issues with This Infrastructure
Single Point of Failure (SPOF):

Ensure each component has redundancy to avoid any single point of failure.
Security Issues (No Firewall, No HTTPS):

Implement firewalls to protect each server and enforce HTTPS for secure communication.
No Monitoring:

Set up monitoring for all servers to track performance and detect issues promptly.
